To start the application
run the main method

REST api details
Only one Rest API is developed for create/update/delete respectively.
Appropriate GameStatus has been included when game is created, decked is added and game is deleted
The changes to the game are tracked by a listener.

Sequence
create game.(default cards per person is 2 and deck 1)
update game(If any deck/person).
dealCards
delete

Once the game is started, the deck or player cannot be updated.
The cards are dealt to each player.
